00:23:44,358 --> 00:23:45,957
Genta is the pig!

413
00:23:45,958 --> 00:23:47,958
Mitsuhiko is the water sprite!

414
00:23:49,258 --> 00:23:52,357
Those are "Son Goku's" characters.

415
00:23:52,358 --> 00:23:56,258
You guys! Then, am I a hot dog?

